<h4 id="did-you-know"><strong>Did you know?</strong></h4>
<ol>
  <li>There is a list of <a href="https://libguides.lib.fit.edu/OEREng/home">Open Textbooks for Engineering</a> curated by Engineering Librarians around the country.</li>
  <li>The Libraries offers full access to <a href="https://guides.library.cmu.edu/az/databases?q=reaxys">Reaxys</a>. Sign up for one of these <a href="https://elsevier.zoom.us/webinar/register/WN_1yGIHrvMShq4EKf4Ytg9gA#/registration">webinars</a> to learn how to use this resource to access chemical literature, patents, substances, and reactions.</li>
</ol>

